{"id":1076465558,"question_id":3,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"8Â months","timestamp":1697439588,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"6 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1076465558/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"43.5 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int lengthOfLongestSubstring(String s) {\n        int res = 0;\n        int len = s.length();\n\n        Set<Character> set =new HashSet<>();\n\n        int st=0;\n        for(int ed=0; ed<len; ed++){\n            char ch = s.charAt(ed);\n\n            while(st<len && set.contains(ch)){\n                set.remove(s.charAt(st++));\n            }\n\n            set.add(ch);\n            res = Math.max(res, ed-st+1);\n        }\n\n        return res;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
